---
const bandMembers = [
    { name: "Scott Ivey", role: "Vocals / Guitar / Piano" },
    { name: "Eric Johnson", role: "Guitar" },
    { name: "Daniel Ellis", role: "Bass" },
    { name: "Brandon Barnes", role: "Drums" }
];
---

<section class="bg-black relative pt-24 pb-24">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 md:gap-20 items-start">
                {/* Left Column - Description */}
                <div class="space-y-12">
                    <div class="space-y-8">
                        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white">About Us</h2>
                        <div class="prose prose-lg prose-invert">
                            <p class="text-white/80 leading-relaxed">
                                Back to the Start is a tribute to Coldplay's earliest and most iconic era, capturing the raw emotion and atmospheric
                                beauty of Parachutes, A Rush of Blood to the Head, and X&Y. With a deep reverence for the original sound, the band
                                delivers an immersive experience that takes audiences on a journey through Coldplay's golden years—from the intimate
                                melancholy of "Sparks" to the soaring anthems like "Clocks" and "Fix You."
                            </p>
                            <p class="text-white/80 leading-relaxed mt-6">
                                Led by vocalist and multi-instrumentalist Scott Ivey, the band features Eric Johnson on guitar, Daniel Ellis on bass, and
                                Brandon Barnes on drums. Together, they channel the spirit, tone, and passion that made Coldplay a global
                                phenomenon—before the stadium synths and pop beats.
                            </p>
                            <p class="text-white/80 leading-relaxed mt-6">
                                Whether you're a lifelong fan or discovering these songs for the first time, Back to the Start brings the heart of early
                                Coldplay to life with authenticity, precision, and soul.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-6">
                        <div class="text-center p-4">
                            <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-2">90</div>
                            <div class="text-sm text-white/60 uppercase tracking-wider">Mins</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="text-center p-4">
                            <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-2">3</div>
                            <div class="text-sm text-white/60 uppercase tracking-wider">Albums</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="text-center p-4">
                            <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-2">2000-05</div>
                            <div class="text-sm text-white/60 uppercase tracking-wider">Era</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                {/* Right Column - Logo */}
                <div class="flex items-center justify-center">
                    <div class="w-full max-w-md space-y-8">
                        <img 
                            src="/white-logo.png" 
                            alt="Back to the Start" 
                            class="w-full hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-700 ease-out hover:brightness-110"
                        />
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    {/* Subtle Gradient Overlay */}
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-black via-transparent to-black opacity-50 pointer-events-none"></div>
</section> 